{"tid":885300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[日經]而家到底重有無學生係講廣東話","createTime":"2018-11-01T08:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T08:55:18.000Z","uid":18604,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e094af0d9dfe2ed0d3ec0ae83f0e65df9b129cfd","tid":885300,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:38:40.000Z","msg":"太和火車站九成學生係用蝗語大大聲講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e033a4b525dd1182f88b5f21dfc250c4c78134","tid":885300,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:40:28.000Z","msg":"依家啲小學生好乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n翻工見果三隻蝗頂係門口掛住吹水阻人上落，已經見過一個後生仔屌過佢地老母幾次<br />\n<br />\n但果三隻垃圾都仲係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89c73bcc2f95c0c666a88a6b5751dad8f42492a","tid":885300,"uid":85633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:42:47.000Z","msg":"一上地鐵成架車都係大陸人<br />\n嗰下我覺得香港已經無得救<br />\n但另一邊係到諗<br />\n只係班蝗會係地鐵大聲鳩叫<br />\n香港人點會咁做<br />\n不過應該都係我唔死心既諗法黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8229bd3544df372989bb76be58434d842c6cb78","tid":885300,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:48:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17ba1958437e810cf875d834d51a16abe9e2a958","tid":885300,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:52:25.000Z","msg":"吊，无拉无拉，香港挽猿拉"},{"pid":"bb3b8b3025b0862a26c402e6df89e07ef708dd05","tid":885300,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8229bd3544df372989bb76be58434d842c6cb78","tid":885300,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8